N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4111.25 - Withdrawals

State Regulations

Where subsequent payments are required, a complete list
of those withdrawn or declared out shall be made within 15 days after payment
was due and the list filed with the commission and mailed to every
nominator. Notes
